entries.entry: Today I learned about using an alias to declare a variable for the terminal, and echo to create a string.
Started first group project. Learned how to push to github, approve and then pull each other's work.
Practiced adding objects to an API and then having them automatically load to the DOM on the push of a button. It took most of the day but I'm proud of the work I did.
Learned how to normalize our json-servers
Have learned a lot, but not enough to do what I want to do.
Learned how to work with many to many relationships
